|{{partial|可选}}
|-
|colspan="2" |在数据库中登记旅行者的出入境记录<br>（'''注意'''：直到2011年十月，只有[[爱沙尼亚|爱沙尼亚]]、[[芬兰|芬兰]]、[[希腊|希腊]]、[[匈牙利|匈牙利]]、[[拉脱维亚|拉脱维亚]]、[[立陶宛|立陶宛]]、[[马耳他|马耳他]]、[[波兰|波兰]]、[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]和[[斯洛伐克|斯洛伐克]]这10个国家会记录出入境记录，但这些记录仅存在于每个国家自己的数据库中，这些记录并没有在申根区的全域系统中被分享或交换）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://eur-lex.europa.eu/LexUriServ/LexUriServ.do?uri=COM:2011:0680:FIN:EN:PDF |title=Communication from the European Commission to the European Parliament and the Council: Communication from the Commission to the European Parliament and the Council, pg. 6 |accessdate=2012年8月11日 |archive-date=2013年3月9日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130309133522/http://eur-lex.europa.eu/LexUriServ/LexUriServ.do?uri=COM:2011:0680:FIN:EN:PDF |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name='Innovation'>{{cite web|url=http://eu2012.dk/en/Meetings/Conferences/Feb/~/media/Files/Conferences/Jan_Mar/Conference%20on%20Innovation%20Border%20Management/Current%20State%20of%20Play%20-%20EU%20Confernce%20on%20Innovation%20Border%20Management.pdf|title=Current state of play in relation to innovation border management in the EU|format=PDF|accessdate=2012年8月11日|archive-date=2012年11月30日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121130193133/http://eu2012.dk/en/Meetings/Conferences/Feb/~/media/Files/Conferences/Jan_Mar/Conference%20on%20Innovation%20Border%20Management/Current%20State%20of%20Play%20-%20EU%20Confernce%20on%20Innovation%20Border%20Management.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name='Entryexit1'>{{cite web |url=http://www.statewatch.org/news/2011/may/eu-council-tcn-exit-entry-recording-questionnaire-replies-8552-09.pdf |title=Council of the European Union: Questionnaire on the possible creation of a system of electronic recording of entries and exits of third country nationals in the Schengen area |format=PDF |accessdate=2012年8月11日 |archive-date=2012年12月19日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121219035919/http://www.statewatch.org/news/2011/may/eu-council-tcn-exit-entry-recording-questionnaire-replies-8552-09.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name='Entryexit2'>{{cite web |url=http://www.statewatch.org/news/2011/may/eu-council-tcn-exit-entry-recording-questionnaire-replies-8552-add2-09.pdf |title=Council of the European Union: Questionnaire on the possible creation of a system of electronic recording of entries and exits of third country nationals in the Schengen area (Replies from Bulgaria, France, Iceland, Italy, Norway and Portugal |format=PDF |4= |accessdate=2012年8月11日 |archive-date=2012年12月19日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121219040346/http://www.statewatch.org/news/2011/may/eu-council-tcn-exit-entry-recording-questionnaire-replies-8552-add2-09.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name='Entryexit3'>{{cite web|url=http://www.statewatch.org/news/2012/mar/eeu-council-schengen-entry-exit-questionnaire-8552-add3-09.pdf|title=Council of the European Union: Questionnaire on the possible creation of a system of electronic recording of entries and exits of third country nationals in the Schengen area (Reply from Greece)|format=PDF|4=|accessdate=2012年8月11日|archive-date=2012年4月12日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120412182303/http://www.statewatch.org/news/2012/mar/eeu-council-schengen-entry-exit-questionnaire-8552-add3-09.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>）
